{"tid":1776872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[求和]  中國望盡快與美達成貿易協議","createTime":"2019-12-09T23:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T03:57:34.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"15afead58ad329deb775d5133d10c03256f1bf87","tid":1776872,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T23:24:28.000Z","msg":"中國望盡快與美達成貿易協議<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/china-says-hopes-it-can-reach-trade-agreement-with-us-as-soon-as-possible-20191209/5198511.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fchina-says-hopes-it-can-reach-trade-agreement-with-us-as-soon-as-possible-20191209%2F5198511.html&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=de8ef665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/china-says-hopes-it-can-reach-trade-agreement-with-us-as-soon-as-possible-20191209/5198511.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中國星期一（12月9日）表示希望能盡快同美國達成一項貿易協議。與此同時，在美國對中國進口商品本週末開始加徵新的關稅之前，雙方正在進行密集的磋商。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國商務部助理部長任鴻斌9日對媒體表示，中國希望盡快取得各方都滿意的談判和磋商結果。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n他說：&ldquo;關於中美經貿磋商和談判，我們希望雙方本著平等和相互尊重的原則推進談判和磋商，也照顧到彼此的核心關切，盡快取得各方都滿意的結果。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n美中兩國目前正在就所謂的第一階段貿易協議進行磋商，旨在緩和雙方長期的貿易爭端，但是，兩國是否能在近期達成一項協議，目前還不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n華盛頓對中國進口商品加徵新一輪的關稅將於12月15日開始實施。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國要求美國取消對大約3750億美元輸美產品目前加徵的部分關稅，此外還要取消定於12月15日對另外大約1560億美元即將加徵的關稅。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普要求中國承諾購買具體最低美國農產品數量，同時在知識產權，人民幣匯率，以及金融市場准入方面做出讓步。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n白宮經濟顧問庫德洛上星期五說，雙方幾乎每天都在進行談判，但是目前雙方沒有計劃舉行面談或特朗普和習近平之間的簽署儀式。<br />\n<br />\n在美中雙方密集談判之間，距離美國擬定的最後期限還有不到一個星期。庫德洛說，特朗普將在涉及中國產的手機、筆記本電腦、玩具和服裝等關稅問題上做出最終決定。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普上星期說：&ldquo;12月15日，可能會發生某些事情，但是我們還沒有討論那個問題。我們在同中國進行非常好的談判。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"71aab5983022a6c613d6e086b8c6846bf5c11efc","tid":1776872,"uid":25858,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T23:27:39.000Z","msg":"一定傾唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcf5d167daf3951cdf24ad46cddb195f3476744","tid":1776872,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T23:28:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔打嗱.jpg！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"eea03054c60c42386d772e3bff00a060423093b4","tid":1776872,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T23:28:21.000Z","msg":"侵仔而家話唔想同你簽"},{"pid":"e508b8adc8d552803e95c4b1abec24f4a9b5ce60","tid":1776872,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dfcf5d167daf3951cdf24ad46cddb195f3476744","tid":1776872,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T23:28:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔打嗱.jpg！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T23:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/da9/098/da9098bc6fae5d09320194727e4cc9a9a344685f_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fda9%2F098%2Fda9098bc6fae5d09320194727e4cc9a9a344685f_n.jpg&h=45d3866c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60014d36359322f57c4b8cf295ea44a7f7a999fc","tid":1776872,"uid":38962,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T23:29:01.000Z","msg":"取消關稅呢個位其實都唔太需要傾"},{"pid":"d8768d3d0bbf95cfacc6c43a2e8074b969bd60b1","tid":1776872,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T23:29:19.000Z","msg":"而家美國經濟數據咁好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！📊📊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"0c0d335feb11bb4c0063451db55b7dd